es defining part of the shape. The data in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"this array is copied to the shape’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"coordinates"},{"type":"text","text":" property."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"coords"}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If the shape is currently visible on the map as an annotation, it is redrawn","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"immediately. If the shape is part of an ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSource","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" object, you must","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"explicitly set the ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSource\/shape","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" property in order for any style","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"layers that use the source to be redrawn.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The number of coordinates in "},{"code":"coords","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" must be equal to the length of "},{"code":"range","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"If you want to insert or delete one or more vertices, use the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"-replaceCoordinatesInRange:withCoordinates:count:","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" method."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"range"},{"type":"text","text":" extends beyond the shape’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"coordinates"},{"type":"text","text":" property, an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NSRangeException"},{"type":"text","text":" is raised. If you want to append new vertices to the shape,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"use the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"-appendCoordinates:count:"},{"type":"text","text":" method."}]}]}],"metadata":{"title":"replaceCoordinatesInRange:withCoordinates:","roleHeading":"Instance Method","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMultiPoint(im)replaceCoordinatesInRange:withCoordinates:","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"replaceCoordinatesInRange:withCoordinates:"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"replaceCoordinatesInRange:withCoordinates:"}],"symbolKind":"method"},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPoint\/replaceCoordinatesInRange:withCoordinates:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Replaces the vertices at the given range in the shape with the same number of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"vertices from a given C array."}],"kind":"symbol","references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNShape":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnshape","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape","fragments":[{"text":"MLNShape","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","title":"MLNShape","abstract":[{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" is an abstract class that represents a shape or annotation. Shapes","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"constitute the content of a map — not only the overlays atop the map, but also","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the content that forms the base map.","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNStyle":{"kind":"symbol","title":"MLNStyle","fragments":[{"text":"MLNStyle","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnstyle","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/doc